Package application.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Deadline
    The Deadline class represents a deadline and the requirement associated with that deadline.
    DeadlineList
    The DeadlineList class represents a container for Deadlines.
    LearningGuide
    The LearningGuide class represents guides that will aid the User in studying.
    Note
    The Note class represents a note that stores information that is important for the user.
    NoteOrganizer
    The NoteOrganizer class represents a container of Notes.
    Playlist
    The Playlist class is a container of Songs.
    Question
    The Question class represents a question on a Quiz.
    Quiz
    The Quiz class represents a test with questions that must be answered by students.
    Song
    The Song class represents a song that can be played on music players.
    Subject
    The Subject class represents a "course" that a student would have to go through in school.
    User
    The User class represents the person who will be using the app; it is similar to an "account." It contains the user's username, grade level, password, and an ArrayList containing all Users.
